						<div class="postbody">There is no hardware limitation on having different times for each frame of an animation. My animation code allows for this, but it does double the size of an animation definition (which isn't really a problem these days).<br /><br />Without bank switching or chr-ram you might run out of tiles to use on other things though.</div>

